    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is a mechanically sound 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the 3.6L flat-six powerplant with VarioCam Plus, delivering 320hp through a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. This chassis exhibits excellent torsional rigidity and remains composed under lateral load thanks to its factory-spec suspension geometry. Recent service includes a borescope inspection and an IMS bearing retrofit for long-term reliability. The hydraulic steering rack offers superb tactile feedback, and the four-piston monobloc Brembo calipers provide consistent deceleration with minimal fade. Finished in Arctic Silver over black leather, this 996 is a driver-focused example ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
