      "description": "This well-cared-for vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only the minor stone chips expected from careful road use. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin featuring supple leather upholstery that has been regularly conditioned and a suite of fully functional technology, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; the engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears, and a comprehensive service history confirms it has never missed a scheduled maintenance appointment. Recently fitted with a fresh set of tires and having passed a multi-point inspection, this car is ready for the road today. It offers a premium driving experience and reliable performance for its next owner.",
